optimized_sql: WITH filtered_item AS (SELECT i_item_sk FROM item WHERE i_category IN ('Children', 'Electronics', 'Music')), filtered_customer_dims AS (SELECT c.c_customer_sk, c.c_first_name, c.c_last_name FROM customer c INNER JOIN customer_address ca ON c.c_current_addr_sk = ca.ca_address_sk INNER JOIN household_demographics hd ON c.c_current_hdemo_sk = hd.hd_demo_sk WHERE ca.ca_state IN ('AR', 'CO', 'NC', 'NY', 'TX') AND hd.hd_income_band_sk BETWEEN 7 AND 13 AND hd.hd_buy_potential = '0-500'), filtered_store_returns AS (SELECT sr.sr_ticket_number, sr.sr_item_sk, d1.d_date_sk AS d1_date_sk, d1.d_date AS d1_date FROM store_returns sr INNER JOIN date_dim d1 ON sr.sr_returned_date_sk = d1.d_date_sk INNER JOIN filtered_item i ON sr.sr_item_sk = i.i_item_sk WHERE d1.d_year = 1998), filtered_web_sales AS (SELECT ws.ws_bill_customer_sk, ws.ws_item_sk, d2.d_date_sk AS d2_date_sk, d2.d_date AS d2_date FROM web_sales ws INNER JOIN date_dim d2 ON ws.ws_sold_date_sk = d2.d_date_sk INNER JOIN filtered_item i ON ws.ws_item_sk = i.i_item_sk) SELECT c.c_customer_sk, c.c_first_name, c.c_last_name, COUNT(*) AS cnt FROM store_sales ss INNER JOIN filtered_store_returns sr ON ss.ss_ticket_number = sr.sr_ticket_number AND ss.ss_item_sk = sr.sr_item_sk INNER JOIN filtered_web_sales ws ON ss.ss_customer_sk = ws.ws_bill_customer_sk AND ss.ss_item_sk = ws.ws_item_sk INNER JOIN filtered_customer_dims c ON ss.ss_customer_sk = c.c_customer_sk WHERE ss.ss_sales_price / ss.ss_list_price BETWEEN 35 * 0.01 AND 55 * 0.01 AND ws.d2_date BETWEEN sr.d1_date AND (sr.d1_date + INTERVAL '90 DAY') GROUP BY c.c_customer_sk, c.c_first_name, c.c_last_name ORDER BY cnt
